# 4. Add `copyFile(...)` to `CosStorageService`

You currently have `moveIfExists(...)` and `moveFile(...)`.
For this retry change, add a simple copy method:

```java
public void copyFile(String sourceKey, String targetKey) {
    s3Client.copyObject(bucketName, sourceKey, bucketName, targetKey);
    log.info("Copied {} -> {}", sourceKey, targetKey);
}
```

If you want safer logging/error handling:

```java
public void copyFile(String sourceKey, String targetKey) {
    try {
        s3Client.copyObject(bucketName, sourceKey, bucketName, targetKey);
        log.info("Copied {} -> {}", sourceKey, targetKey);
    } catch (Exception e) {
        throw new IllegalStateException("Failed to copy " + sourceKey + " to " + targetKey, e);
    }
}
